ipchains (1.3.10-13) unstable; urgency=medium

  * The init.d script causes so many problems and resolves so some, it's
    not reasonable to have a such script. I decided to remove it. All
    who need that script will have to add the it by hand. Sorry guys.
  * Init 1 doesn't kill /etc/ipchains.save anymore. (closes: Bug#116136)
  * Emacs-thingy removed from this changelog.

